data.title: Gertrud Anna Gertrude "Gertrude Anne" of Hohenberg Queen Consort of Germany (± 1225
data.meta_description: Gertrud Anna Gertrude of Hohenberg was born about 1225, daughter of Burchard von Hohenberg and Mechtild von Tübingen. She was married in the year 1245 in Habsburg,Aargau Canton,Switzerland to Rudolf I von Habsburg, they gave birth to 1 child. She died on February 16, 1281. This information is part of Stamboom by M. K. on Genealogy Online.
